As one of the head of Hospitality training in the world , Switzerland has been a best destination for Vietnamese student lately . How is the life of a oversea student in Swiss ? What should we prepare for studying abroad ? That is the reason for holding the seminar “ THE_SWISS_LIFE_FOR_OVERSEAS_STUDENT” hosted by Vietnam_Hospitality_Network ( VHN ) and Business_Hotel & Management_School ( BHMS ) . Our seminar will mention these contents :
> > > Education in Switzerland
> > > Training program of BHMS
> > > Life in Switzerland
> > > Career development after graduation in Switzerland
This seminar will give you an opportunity to listen and discuss with top experts about what you need to know when studying in Switzerland .
* * * Ms . Thongsawai_Pornumar – Regional_Manager .
* * * Ms . Phan_Thi_Bich_Phuong - Representatives of the BHMS in Vietnam .
